caption: This is my spot right after I pay off my charge card from CHASE Bank. I love their many sub sandwiches, their salads, Love-Love their in- house baked cookies. The big Sugar and the Oatmeal Raisin cookies. The shakes are amazing too! Update: 3-24-21 Since I have joined their Potbelly Perks Rewards. For my Birthday I received a treat $5.00 off for a dessert of my choice. *But you have to add it with a meal. So, I chose 1 Chocolate Shake. With my *Mediterranean Salad fixed my way No Chickpeas, No Red Peppers. It was delicious. Thank You, Potbelly

I work up the road at Mattress Firm. We work 10 hour days and if we are solo we can't leave to get lunch. Needless to say we all frequent this location. It's Labor Day weekend and I've been sick all week. When I ordered my lunch today over the phone with Christine, I mentioned I wasn't feeling well. When my order arrived a short while later there was an envelope with a card and cookies that read "Hope you feel better soon <3 Christine". At Mattress Firm we call that a Moment of Truth. It made my freaking day and put a smile on my face. I've never had anything but polite and speedy service from this location. Keep hiring people like Christine! She's awesome.
